

=Bio=

"Guy Janssen is a governance advisor and a political economist with more than 25 years of experience in 16 countries. His strength is to align forces that stimulate and sustain change. He works on institutional reform, government process re-engineering, power structures, strategic analysis, incentives, and change management in any field. He has an MPhil in International Political Economy, an MA in International and European Relations, and an MSc in Computer Engineering. Guy has a particular interest in agile planning, open source development and self-organization. He is now dedicated to ensuring that moja global is an open, transparent, responsive, innovative and efficient organisation."

